    "body": "Problem: <Esc> in a Select-mode tabstop leaves the session and highlight active. CursorMoved isn’t triggered since the cursor doesn’t move.\r\n\r\nSolution: use ModeChanged (s:n) instead. Defer with vim.schedule() to avoid transient s:n from jump().\r\n\r\nFix #39220\r\n",
